类 InitialScenarioGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • initialization.InitialScenarioGenerator

  • public class InitialScenarioGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides methods to outprint initial scenarios, which can be copy-pasted to an .ini file, and once filled can be loaded by InitialScenario.load()
    作者:
    He Xiaoan, Ji Raymond
